    "description": {
        "en-US": "This extension allows you to automatically use your signature from Gmail accounts in Thunderbird. No longer need to maintain two separated signatures!\n\nYou can select a Gmail account for every Thunderbird account. Signatures are synced on app startup, or when you click a button on the options page.\n\n<b>Attention!</b> This is still a beta version. Please report any troubles. In addition, <b>you need to configure your own OAuth credentials in Google</b>. This is described on a <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://github.com/kam193/thbrd-signature/wiki/Registering-own-OAuth-app-in-Google\">wiki page</a>. I hope this difficulty will be gone soon."
    },
